This paper is primarily focused on wireless sensor networks, which suggests that it is likely to be categorized under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also deals with security issues related to outlier detection, which could place it under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The use of data streams and dynamic updates suggests that it could also be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DB (Databases). Finally, the paper's focus on energy consumption and power management suggests that it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
